{"tid":534711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"M巾包毒品 鬼祟Benz男女斷正","createTime":"2018-01-20T06:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T06:04:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e933e578a8b2544906836e8540c87665a82ee008","tid":534711,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180120/20280618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280618&d=Gp8aH3skem65Oem7sUL1dsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=845a6df3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F20280618&h=d913204c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180120/20280618</a><br />\n<br />\nM巾包毒品<br />\n鬼祟Benz男女斷正<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一輛停泊在尖沙嘴麼地道K11對開的平治房車，昨晨5時許，司機瞥見警員巡邏車，立即開車，引起可疑，遭截停搜查。<br />\n<br />\n車上有男司機及女乘客，警員搜查下發現，前座手枕位有一包毒品，隨即召來警犬搜車，結果在車尾廂再有發現。歹徒將一包毒品用紙巾包住，再用一片衞生巾包裹遮掩，撿獲的毒品包括有60克「冰」毒及少量懷疑第一部毒藥，總值約24,000元。男司機姓楊48歲，女乘客姓范25歲，涉嫌販毒被捕，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進。"}]}